  <brief_title>Hyperbaric Oxygen in Lower Leg Trauma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Hyperbaric Oxygen Reduce Complications and Improve Outcomes After Open Tibial Fractures With Severe Soft Tissue Injury? An International Multi-centre Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
