  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Acute phase complication rate</measure>
    <time_frame>14 days post trauma</time_frame>
    <description>The primary outcome measure will be the incidence of acute complications after injury. This is a composite measure we define as the occurrence within two weeks of trauma of one or both of: significant soft tissue necrosis developing after the initial surgery or significant wound infection.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
